Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:45.25,effect,effect,0,0,0,,{\frz-8.2\frx9\fry-6\move(517,443,554,395)\distort(1.01,0,0.999,0.95,.0,1)\blur0.5}從今以後，將利用這個線路通訊。
